    {
      "text": "Victory Road, released as Dogō Sōken in Japan and also known as Ikari Warriors II: Victory Road, is a run and gun video game developed and published by SNK for arcades. It was released in Japan in 1986 and North America in 1987 by Tradewest. The game is a sequel to Ikari Warriors, released earlier the same year.",
